    FAQs


Smarter financial tools to give you a strategic advantage

    Smart plaintiff's attorneys use every available advantage in court. The smarter financial tools of RD Legal Funding can give you a significant strategic advantage in building your firm.
    

    We understand the unique financial challenges faced by plaintiff's attorneys. Your cases often require large amounts of capital to pursue - but it can take months or even years to collect your fees. Our Attorney's Line of Credit and Fee Acceleration solutions are designed specifically to meet your financial needs and provide the resources you need to take your firm to the next level.
    

    Even if you've never used a funding source before...even if you feel you don't have an urgent need for cash...we can show you why our programs make smart business sense.
    


Attorney Fee Acceleration

    Our proprietary program that converts settled cases into immediate cash. No more waiting for slow-paying defendants, administrative delays, or court approvals.
            

Fees advanced on almost any type of settlement
                Access immediate cash from $53,000 to $20 million
                No monthly interest payments
                No points or upfront fees to pay
                No restrictions on how you use the cash
                We even assume the risk of the defendant's non-payment!
            

apply now
            Complete our Fee Acceleration Application.




Attorney's Line of Credit

    The money you need...when you need it!
            

Lines up to $10 million or more
                Maximize income and cash flow
                Use for any purpose
                Interest accrues only on outstanding funds
            

apply now
            Download our Line of Credit Application.


Plaintiff Settlement Funding

    Are you a plaintiff with a settled case, but tired of waiting to get paid? RD Legal now offers non-recourse post-settlement funding to plaintiffs. Read More.

