Diversified Financial Services

Company Overview of RD Legal Funding, LLC



Snapshot People




Company Overview
RD Legal Funding, LLC provides financial solutions to the legal industry in the United States. Its solutions include Attorney Fee Acceleration, a program that converts settled cases into immediate cash; Attorney's Line of Credit, a credit line for various purposes; and Plaintiff Settlement Funding program for non-recourse post-settlement funding. The company offers solutions for various types of settlements that include personal injury, medical malpractices, negligence, wage and hour disputes, wrongful death, infant injuries, court appointed fees, class actions, employment discrimination, securities class actions, product liability, mass torts, antitrust, and court-appointed fees. RD Legal F...
RD Legal Funding, LLC provides financial solutions to the legal industry in the United States. Its solutions include Attorney Fee Acceleration, a program that converts settled cases into immediate cash; Attorney's Line of Credit, a credit line for various purposes; and Plaintiff Settlement Funding program for non-recourse post-settlement funding. The company offers solutions for various types of settlements that include personal injury, medical malpractices, negligence, wage and hour disputes, wrongful death, infant injuries, court appointed fees, class actions, employment discrimination, securities class actions, product liability, mass torts, antitrust, and court-appointed fees. RD Legal Funding was founded in 1997 and is based in Cresskill, New Jersey.
